act.article:
2 Definitions.—
1 In these rules, unless the context otherwise requires,—
a “Act” means the Commission of Sati (Prevention) Act, 1987 (3 of 1988);
b “prohibitory order” means an order issued under section 6;
c “section” means section of the Act.
2 Words and expressions used but not defined in these rules and defined ‘in the Act shall have the same meanings as are respectively assigned to them in the Act.
